  "detailed_description": "<h1>OUR OTHER GAMES</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154590/extras/53e11c9c9f894374eb314cd6b91ed5e0.avif?t=1771688452\" width=600 height=192 /></span><br><br>100 Find Kitties: Pirates is a hidden objects/clicker game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh no! The ship commanded by Captain Red-whisker, the most dangerous pirate cat that ever sailed on the sardine-salmon sea, was attacked by an underwater monster with tentacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 130 pirate crew cats on the map. Your task is to point out all of them on the map. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many games where we look for hidden cats, but have you ever looked for grotesque cat pirates?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-130 funny cats to find </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-hand-drawn graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-cat-pirates</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3154590/extras/e5bc324547f256e3c1d19e58cf9b2b7e.avif?t=1771688452\" width=600 height=192 /></span></p>",
